OL,5,G0000 Scam City: Don't Get Caught Out!
OL,6,     FIn Istanbul, a friendly
OL,7,     Fconversation at night may lead to
OL,8,     Fa bar bill of hundreds or even
OL,9,     Fthousands. If you can't pay,
OL,10,     Fyou're threatened with violence.
OL,11,G0105 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,12,     FThe doctors of Hall Green Health
OL,13,     Fcome face to face with some rare
OL,14,     Fconditions. It's a reminder that
OL,15,     Fwhen you're a GP, you never know
OL,16,     Fwhat is going to walk through your
OL,17,     Fdoor.
